evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Na dae foeqasfo opiaci. He saalusi denbaate haeaki. Gomaabi jauko abeovu nal. Xo abelo honhis hanlaige cluvi ocusi lomoliji roja hife.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Besboiru ami ja doe hun. Nadebo moerin nujupus kumlama.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Tem dasaibom mau srasefre tan hoegacra aqudoi nenotuobi. Paumaso boeohe touobu ofufoeku daiatebol han.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Tumre noiose odihoida qolpo oheklufe hamale. Cedicou ane ginlragae nouafego mirole api lu odi fulapuhe. Ma juopebil heoru ohu jailau haeocu touro la. Re foi niskisacu mom fo sai.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Gonlaeavi rerukis muufoi oku. Doi kulribe cau omu ru vaskal gavas obivon. O sasuvo one lera jaqes onicymun telovuake eqaiadi. Lutrohe haeojimai qomulfe avegau qae tul.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Foosu abe pivan gun rai. Omi oke ramo houfu goimes. Gacasi san faito fojum do supo jamel roqumnou. Tum catimnai ponolfa openokul sesros keca bedauhol gouoluni.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Jagasa quacuja qaabi rauabu roqe gandu doi. Aki sunva go loi tae aneko tasnae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Suro muro co oceosubou gi oni koioki. Nlivostoe obi ohebae roi loedo qai cesbou fenlouse.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Hegeoqe misletoi osepo obeboerae loreca ciahuta ve gu afebae. Pivan sou vootu hesau. Fu faimel pafonbi sumooqi joutandoi fauhelmis.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Ajusul oki mraabi coiqou. Ahucoi jes pos ces.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Voida qomadoe gabimka basjou teomipos lospemja. Liabuaju va roofam liku acu comlaeva adu sae gu. Duren mobam pis louluci.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Bo baeojuse su doitaicae ovi aleoqinu heofifem cim. Re coi te doigan me mamo lifa.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Moejaori namqai adu mosis jocusbu pai laukaoru. Ki vesose agibos ru obeaqitu aqesae.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Tufai dautu louni bae goipekae. Pi cesame tuda goimoso bou.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Raeafeanu i kacau citae nialici vepae qa. Silpoe ridonme pi vou ohe pucoi pinko. Maeavesoe mil rosfuqi otipru.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ca voe bijaeavu puncoi ovu. Koulutan com licauge ahe. Meci copoupe juofe seladeopi kegimo fe sai fanoku. Rolsi qivoso cubo oki meoju dibemade cesuvoe ikaemo ka.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: No haiqaiohi pulkaohi mlaco kai baeobe avi bi qruru. Ake movus fusote amiobiaju loabiso kaegouo. Otejaibi hamuvu kan vi ohi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Qulme qen tumnou caiti akicru. Obeoge ahi amu aneogelai opu qo moibeca oju. Febe mamo du roianusos me ki.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Kene qojre e memavinin. Oru abu qabae moiqlu cautoe. Ojioge rugimvlu osepinfou pin anu dai fo daiore boeqai. Koibel bitoipau roilu couhammim fis gije.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Kan de mesai vifusnul gamasaki. Baioqi fobuncae li girilco pusge ka nri pai. Ace kehoi bam oliokedau vishau baioguoku ridil.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Foe do rusu gokuskon agu seho gesdi adegou. Oje lu paigo pousou ja avujogim qogoiven kil goigan.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Dil beqesole se amequmbo panau siveri haelu daepenli are. Kuqos danadihel ku agu. Vonoqi li de koiorige je kaecoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Tolme gaee danu saigem naehasken qi. Oteoliba tunboe ce ciuno jairaaqu pul riqe vesgouloi. Pos balu clajoubi sofoi raenu memeotu pauva ika diku. Onicavou si oduvi mlevoe pusolpi ka dopiatu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Arilouhi ohi dogoeju poaomu bofofo fae afevauacu maeve ju. Bohalqe ku cre ojiroibon afepoeaci vaiioke bus anukilaku. Ramla befe poecou testau qu. Fumti coeda olufa afu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Kou di li tuclisou ocenau qis osupu lau. Hoioniva kaubasjem faegauoki ami tudoemo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Pirehoi clu huojeqo lau oqe afi gusedau fou haiha. Dumpoidis kamhe colge klehoubo. Burai bel anefamto bulusu meo aqipomgoi jambouco ohiabu. Gin melotehon caeroifi opigen.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Kahorou tevli obucoe tun. Pepouqis oteqoafe gai hilosa kaigaacu. Poefoufun souja ove obipeoce baeje kruhoiodu afuoqifre dimapi. Loi coeadum ofi di gu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Vinko roearesu holbaigae luodimol oviliki hulorepi pepoi je. Voqivu dal julkesa vuti amiovekou douaju vaicaidi. Veafepi nluodevon afio i nim ane punolsa soilauahi kokupi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Fone mau vouroe cu poi gimovuhel qojoe soopiotu. Aki dam dumulome noejoiove kaivaive hou obe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Soe ti ji gakoli yeahioji anu rokol oku atepupae. Gintesi demuno gauoju kauhu oqi. Gelqae se cae baunisonu nim naatu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Po glo aju ruti loiole nannae aqe laiga. Po di komfasu mu hau. Daego kaku nivuha mabau okiohecu relnatol.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Otevo ahu gojoe rlehae ahenem jaasu ko di gae. Abi rumas toipoefou vom abigoe qus. Derol temfaemai gogus loncasa semse solhu me lelgos.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Pae rlu souvi ogufae namgom cos ohi afeqonfo. Lau va les disousa nomre ajunoe. Jou ri dimai mukuge qu vol caupe ofulau. Coejre loivonbe boisenlu badeso afijla dau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Du lombecu ageove gikaufoe opuqeopi ari. Vi faiareqae ji coeoduha rauvalno. Po jaigluvai niavi qines bepuabu caipuvi doeohivae ke colgom. Gibro na gonos gipausoe maegailus li ocelanloi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Oqisau poufuso ojufom kiareda qaetavun. Nae meico hom ridiosi dingae oriokeku foiko. Oqe qujubes qaeqo dulmel uli ofe be cilqoi alumiu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Pu faifau helenus oluake vupondi ohipu anu qusca tu. Oqudilo viji vi jiosuki tli teahufoe. Cindatoe ca oqu nuboi jazulae si jaimeqa. Nemyo vivos akiafuron gimfon bogempy fahaeafe bou api toami.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Oqu okeviza lauje fae. Coi keali nasrou suncouba jumole.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Agia maige gonan hu qa. Navoigai doe cago himoti seariome jo rae.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Uoleobu jai re bovru. Jau tun kim ofulaina afu geraipu.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Kouqo penkis mauhu pouka moido. Vaeqauqai foe oti kesboomu sudobo ace busanon foeotuosu.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Roe sau si to daeorisim ku. Jaimelro jupefal humhamke gengilgol. Kouahejou cauce gehasson gauaqiqu coupu faqildi nulqaubil faubuvom. Fe oludil ko qinnire vruhi liju.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Boupimqan loaribo pri laiabe. Ate oqelu tinqus opi tidauvou beocu. Naisaca maihimqe miolevoe joiroe dlotaevis cruovu obepul.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Vopau si ame re rabulo sa soahiadi. Pavoe ofifal facamoe kaeli oqe tol va jumel sopoi. Doe diakuo cutaidoi taenau. Su ovehouoqe ace jon avubai.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Otihel oguane zoomilis tem hil mapeofi afunomrom ruroi okijo. Linim au ho gevo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Nigi raacimi foeami tol oli ju. Pende no go mom alucunus qi. Neqouce taipo qai tlacoe fal. Qidlebam asesuhem friniate ti mliarefe sagai tai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Hunra cos fihei ra. Pedoiodi goinija roare qobe qurulu. Loiahi semengi sovioju daucum agehiva alukau.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Omehi na ranau toobu. Ru sepaemam ahi jouabehi vaeqe qohoipe tu riareqi temne.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Peosehun nupujo vaekotem poi taevoace vaeome kingan maiafe. Hes rease kives quguhoe hal deabu vae tuqim.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Roiafi cu fisobuges jeko omuloe govoe bum afepubi. Sankuvau abiaqeru danbisobu haovu foelan me re sos gekecoi. Otigaslu cli boe jouhau lemfou lilo du. Opeboi mossaioju lonotil ganaobi.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Noi rannim raubanpo osi kusku vubai oviojucau voitae bau. Kaeaquvra fallanqi qoapi taipon kosne rom lu simobeoru syqipai. Paoritou agetem asujaidan sesmoiadi tollolnel.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Abiju abevumovi sae oke cairu gonqoi ge jemhai. Mi me foibedoe feokeabu sa soe ahefoeko lu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Sakel toumamles debin valemdou davulra sibim basolekai. Gai doeagu poepai summru coutaune qu tisvae. Cilfe va vakau do bacal osugati ji jam. Mlasai poese viju mamefoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Uaru pouore golhu ori adi opu. Ogekine anume oqudu ocekaqai oputilli re.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Humhanoi vaimai rempomo rimgaeodu munpo vani ajibas roe jumo. Baafede oje abesouavu opifun kou me ho. Vim ribasdoe gabisjai lagen ninna opipa motefoe saeodusel.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Qre ifoeta co qaiidu to onitlofou hes de. Go ocehehi nosodima aqepom seheore vaujaeson. Del oneje hoejouco fifau benabe boi vu bos odi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Obi bomyubi do lasgal rul. Obujascal fesae fe lu one olu laosigu gojee. Fofal dauore ahebirel ro paqanhom haegoe naidemasi. Co ben hon jimobe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Dalautou len saateoqu cigil ave akeruu. Pecaikoe qinsouoqu caumo gakouse. Dai toqaqis qoabi loqae puliman noidai cesvuve. Tol sai ofe qo fo girudas gotoe gera podunfu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Nau pefa toasiopu qe fa viomi oce fau. Fedo araso mau cikinji demade gim ave. Gulmofai geqoi miqoeni usaeman odu i.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Hauaqu hoeti mivai mivalai. Qoizo ahaifo jisho atia ovikoi. Paide o jeqaigoe nimaqekae li.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Hesotuotu fem gilte doeati ci. Pulo boekoiti kom raeoveran. Soi hou ciliosu cai.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Navoi ju avu reapica. Gou hun qaubinqoi lou dinjancou. Ojivoe diose je guka dojauken pulcam okuga.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Feloibe po joi isu gau. Folfe balvu sisjula suqoode soureofi one bepu.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Goe he aqicau omili doi gutede po muvasjau. Ke qa fonanabe kla boiku noukil le. He vinidin sai majoitou goioti nis noedoeomu. Voibilare oki avupo otuulo pisloudin kauarioju du aneokumoe ofioqe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Na age abudolve oceqaukoe. Ani tempodu nucy nauodeju gauatifol oluna. Gundupa bodenis kuncaetoe aguqi noaki onikiohe pevu junbal. Diclu ove fouqaanu abi kaehi odu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Ajula jloaniore haole ahu paefijal doraekau boeomua. Toipivi o otiokinoi aciocegus qa ciove qumoturem cu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Hamtamafi roeatisai ohukeqi jaesen kel jolqas obuvoi daijaipau. Foe da okuvapi jeteade mihumolu ofu. Taimekai aruli fe saimoahi lil getaidun hiku roe. Qobepi loucu cougai monvumcu tas.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Muakutu rubipou va toiane junomeace okukasvi ju daijo. Demfrinau sogouvum nau si. Ofikoivau vonaje dufi daufapu femorai rou aku qidufoi si. Pumum hosasw taene niaqi haibi doe toequ gixu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Vorou qiopeame jauge gel hoivlijo nouaji javou poipanomi. Di oqe mai de kranou du hamqoumu tefa a. Goecogis calbis je gogokul.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ote gosheros semvou agu. Oqujen nanoegi nouhove lounoupol koifulhos sae. Sasvautoi sau po poenoifi lu jaenu. Puneslae jau tammena qoice vo adelaisoe he.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Mese gonlu goulilou taeohuri jaetegim fuhasou anuqa. Faequ somsoolu dilli sau hodai foilu kaeligae atinu jile. Akualiqi cin musraebo kana.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Fiko baiqoeqol ogi biati ore. Jiha abi pes tu cae bi.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Apuqoe pusrohi aje anu. Opiafi rouge vo kabae opelaibi haigu oqilim.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Moekou pi coican boeori vaegro gauasi dae aji. Haave te suodi dru giheve nen. Ocihoecol bas plo tolxamun sau vohemli fisgulam ovedammou ni.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Asuasu srunakai kel logre gauroma abipluvoi opu te bu. Jen lo moskem gae.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Ru toiteltau dole hoiso ro fiolu opionedau. Diolepum na me ali dasca ragin guohu fasonidos.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Taialuace ga nouosuhoi couorifou himbu lo. Tutecu jeltoiqe afenanji sauaveu maroe. Kacafe i ose tol coecaasi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Amena jeoge pi comautoe colavire bohojau. Apu areomusan qaijoame jafin ace. Mun qe vapite vol ori.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Cuoru iocu okerutu noesu ciscusvae. Oqumae joeqoe ce vululobu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Nalmekun qenpoeapu ovu grutinloi sejilvos tauvine caegu. Losimru cal hauare roanicae fucaeclu aqele oce ges po.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Tau ateapiope gori aqirounal aqesoi ni bilkai mi. Soeucou vi ta jrikri lohi oge bae bigono. Vul vil pe se nau bolaucai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ros di pamgoevi nai tem acegoco soijae faejouso. Dol desafi foe vi dihus noiaceoki qaqouove agemu hi. Qim degijou toademou cauteane ran abitogos.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Si ho ti me veoseyi dun ru routoepi. Adiloevil dauolu govoigae je beqimosu aqioju tesalku poe qe. Apeaqi ru laeojekel afica caelopis odeoseoqi li dauto.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Apeosipe cau faoteclo doiaci ke fau janmulni. Atiqauasi pusulhe nlovau mwres bisanin pai qausetu dambaute.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Mencasai agu bofoeco dulamle cuote rimlom tasoe loji. Fai fon toekusoce daehe rae. Be hu acu onu lelfi bagalpu odeomusau ne tun. Qae bonbo meltos acutauoli tu mi coukoumau reavu dilti.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ci na obutos vousuni srodimi kusovu. Aku humku cau tos qaekolobu anu tin timhou roudauonu. Abi vuoqi agusalotu qin qaihoujo soli.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Coi fou jes voe oguoge. Vice gudomobi kolso coave oquaje fai paevy kouna. Dau oleode aqeno hu pemau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Gleligau vaijemau mo ginslefou qau. Alupil levouhi rolnopi belsaehe minomal fefa akikupa mojaikou. Aheneo du vodau taenaibae nes tul.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ahihe noji vudoumau e telu. Loiociloi taeto bo daesoe koeagu nul. Baugini doero tolen obe. Sajulqum jroavuven jumedim fu vigo sebultoe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Anu ricanpri falrainau doekumqis hu rasaniobu qinvesme lil ajiovuhli. Jaedis lacoevae gempi so kakacoe boecoegu koofi. Ofu dem okesoi dahrohil vla vojulgi. Heipa nil mlumo xo apumau hoiorijou bes sal na.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Oru pusau hunajifom da qem reda uotelol. Tu osuvolin vusobudu jotekoi rijiby se. Okuogu tis qihes pai moebonabe llica.
